CASE WHEN COALESCE(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.OPEN_DT,' ') <>' 'THEN  to_date(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.OPEN_DT, 'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE NULL END AS OPEN_DT
CASE WHEN COALESCE(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.MATURITY_DT,' ') <>' 'THEN  to_date(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.MATURITY_DT, 'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE NULL END AS MATURITY_DT
CASE WHEN COALESCE(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.CLOSE_DT,' ') <>' 'THEN  to_date(V5DS_LIMIT_INFO.CLOSE_DT , 'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE NULL END AS CLOSE_DT
